    <taskbody>
        <steps>
            <step>
                <cmd>Click on the <cmdname>Validate</cmdname> button on the
                        <?oxy_delete author="megansellmer" timestamp="20150331T092139-0700" content="toolbar.document"?><?oxy_insert_start author="megansellmer" timestamp="20141007T200119-0700"?>toolbar..<?oxy_insert_end?><image
                        placement="break"
                        href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A9eaec41d-3d54-400b-a6ed-70b8ac2f133d/datastream/OBJ/view"
                        id="image_n4q_qxw_mp" align="center"/></cmd>
                <stepresult>If the document is invalid a pop-up appears with error messages.<image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A0af0261a-a586-4bc6-b4f3-e0192cf88f86/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_ws3_bcv_tp" align="center"></image></stepresult>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Click on one of the errors, this will highlight the error in the document. You can then correct the invalid structure.<image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3Aaaf8620d-af69-488b-b3f5-0a1cd9f72d42/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_uxy_fg2_lp" align="center" height="4in" width="6in"></image></cmd>
                <info>You can still save the document if it is invalid, but a pop-up will appear making sure that you want to proceed.<?oxy_attributes align="&lt;change type=&quot;inserted&quot; author=&quot;megansellmer&quot; timestamp=&quot;20141016T125107-0700&quot; /&gt;" placement="&lt;change type=&quot;modified&quot; oldValue=&quot;inline&quot; author=&quot;megansellmer&quot; timestamp=&quot;20141016T125110-0700&quot; /&gt;"?><image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A9f75316d-ee4c-47cb-80ad-4a54e646dc81/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_u5r_2cv_tp" align="center"></image></info>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Validate again.</cmd>
            </step>
        </steps>
        <result>If you fixed all the validation errors, you should receive a confirmation message.<image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3Aa8685a26-4017-401d-869a-d21d09dd9be6/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_tdf_jcv_tp" align="center"></image>
